\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*
Vice-Ridden and Virtuous 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Neither Maou nor Luminous may purchase either Vice-Ridden or Virtuous [CofD
 46], as they use different Anchors.
 The 
